This directory contains files that are used through out URBI projects.

* Components
** hash.hh
Hash tables.  Relies on either G++'s or MS'.

** lockable.hh.
class urbi::Lockable and macro BLOCKED.

** semaphore.hh.
class urbi::Semaphore.

** thread.hh.

